{"tid":1514061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家繼續十點鳩叫 繼續燃點希望","createTime":"2019-08-28T14:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T13:41:35.000Z","uid":180199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d4336841af2433f6cec6dd937470453ec40dde1f","tid":1514061,"uid":180199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"今日聽到我屋邨原來有人叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先小妹同媽咪#metoo集會番到屋邨就聽到有人叫<br />\n咁我就即刻係屋企樓下回應番個巴打<br />\n然後又大叫多句「香港人加油」就跑走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為之前比藍絲係地鐵恐嚇過<br />\n所以好驚比人打<br />\n之後入𨋢好多人<br />\n我媽係度笑我洗咩驚<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪我個舉動太好笑<br />\n突然有個姐姐話：阿妹 你咁叫唔得架 要對住窗口叫先傳到周圍<br />\n我個刻真係好滾動 聽頭個句以為係鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完之後眼濕濕咁笑住點頭 話我聽日再試<br />\n<br />\n最後出𨋢仲有個哥哥同我講：期待聽日聽到你把聲<br />\n真係好開心原來大家都支持<br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好睇少呢個鳩叫 <br />\n真係可以比到力量各位手足<br />\n係抗爭到好攰好絕望嘅時候比到力量各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"8b4f8f5c610183f30884400dc5436c8ea394a231","tid":1514061,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:49:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85c67e2639a5e6868cd8fe81ed15cc312421b79c","tid":1514061,"uid":180199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"希望大家繼續叫啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a20fd0bc0d09ea39041e3f0cf5000f88e7493c","tid":1514061,"uid":257860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f442c93b61b639dd817199de78fe3eec155a2d97","tid":1514061,"uid":287830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:57:33.000Z","msg":"頭先係地鐵站聽到有人大叫<br />\n嚇左一嚇<br />\n不過真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfb64b42cc0000e0d0191389cc872168d82f1b8","tid":1514061,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGbnrz0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGbnrz0.gif&h=dd99b35f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Cu4EU1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Cu4EU1.gif&h=5bf81da8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a336c1885b731f5725a4865f33a79c9eb0c2d38","tid":1514061,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同我<br />\n十點鐘大叫 香港人  831 遮打見</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCBypV8.gif&h=d3183b47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCBypV8.gif\" data-thumbnail-sr